  "across all procedure fields (I10_PR1 through I10_PR25) in both the correct ",
  "Peripheral Nervous System section (01QM0ZZ, 01QM3ZZ, 01QM4ZZ) and the ",
  "Central Nervous System section (00QM0ZZ, 00QM3ZZ, 00QM4ZZ), the latter ",
  "serving as a coding-error detection query. National estimates were ",
  "calculated using NIS discharge weights (DISCWT) with NIS_STRATUM ",
  "stratification and HOSP_NIS clustering per HCUP analytic guidance.\n\n",

  "RESULTS (NIS paragraph):\n",
